Name: Cat Dungeon Escape
About the game: Cat Dungeon Escape is a hard challenging Puzzle Game with some precision platform elements!! Rotate the Scene and invert the gravity for to get the key , open the door and escape !! With several traps along the way, this can be more difficult than you think !!! HARD CHALLENGING PUZZLE WITH PRECISION PLATFORM ELEMENTS The first levels are simple just to get used to the idea of ​​the game , and than it is getting hard level by level.. Perfect for Hard Game Lovers To take the key will be not so simple !! Fire traps , spikes , portals and more are waiting for you !! GAMEPLAY The Gameplay is really simple and easy !! Use the keys 'A' and 'D' to rotate screen and 'SPACE' to invert gravity !!! FEATURES Manipulate gravity Rotate scene Easy gameplay The challenge increases with each level Pixel Art Game Challenging Puzzle 50 Levels Precision platform elements
